    public class ApacheHttpAsyncClient
extends ThrottledHttpClient<org.apache.http.client.methods.HttpUriRequest,org.apache.http.HttpResponse>
    An asynchronous HttpClient which sends HttpUriRequest and registers a callback. It encapsulates a CloseableHttpClient instance to send the HttpUriRequest CloseableHttpAsyncClient is used
